#. MyMassiveHeatSink.STRINGS.BUILDINGS.PREFABS.MYMASSIVEHEATSINK.NAME
msgctxt "MyMassiveHeatSink.STRINGS.BUILDINGS.PREFABS.MYMASSIVEHEATSINK.NAME"
msgid "<link=\"MYMASSIVEHEATSINK\">反熵热量中和器</link>"
msgstr "<link=\"MYMASSIVEHEATSINK\">Neutralisateur Thermique Anti-Entropie</link>"

#. MyMassiveHeatSink.STRINGS.BUILDINGS.PREFABS.MYMASSIVEHEATSINK.EFFECT
msgctxt "MyMassiveHeatSink.STRINGS.BUILDINGS.PREFABS.MYMASSIVEHEATSINK.EFFECT"
msgid ""
"一种自我维持的机器，似乎由精炼的中子质供能。\n"
"当提供管道氢气时，会吸收并中和热量。"
msgstr ""
"Une machine autonome qui semble etre alimentee par du neutronium raffine.\n"
"Lorsqu'elle est alimentee en hydrogene via des conduites, elle absorbe et "
"neutralise la chaleur."

#. MyMassiveHeatSink.STRINGS.BUILDINGS.PREFABS.MYMASSIVEHEATSINK.DESC
msgctxt "MyMassiveHeatSink.STRINGS.BUILDINGS.PREFABS.MYMASSIVEHEATSINK.DESC"
msgid "一个可配置的反熵热量中和器。"
msgstr "Un neutralisateur thermique anti-entropie configurable."

#. MyMassiveHeatSink.STRINGS.K24M24GG24H0_UI.UI_1
msgctxt "MyMassiveHeatSink.STRINGS.K24M24GG24H0_UI.UI_1"
msgid "降温效果"
msgstr "Effet de refroidissement"

#. MyMassiveHeatSink.STRINGS.K24M24GG24H0_UI.UI_2
msgctxt "MyMassiveHeatSink.STRINGS.K24M24GG24H0_UI.UI_2"
msgid "设置反熵热量中和器的每秒降温效果"
msgstr "Definit le refroidissement par seconde du neutralisateur thermique"

